<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>outcomestar — Every outcome. One star.</title>
<meta name="description" content="Stop scrambling senior fall. One longitudinal record for your child's whole journey — academics, athletics, activities, applications — kept by you, from first milestones to college admission.">
